tags: the force is strong with this one
summary:
The grocery store I shop at put up this chocolate display for the holiday season.
It's cute. Peace in a bunch of languages....
body:
So I noticed a thing…

The grocery store I shop at put up this chocolate display for the holiday season.

It’s cute. Peace in a bunch of languages. Sure. Nice sentiment.

But wait.

What’s that there?

SITH FUCKING CHOCOLATE

Not only does the dark side have cookies, but entire chocolate bars as well.

No wonder so many are tempted.

Would’ve been funnier if it were dark chocolate though.

Apparently evil tastes like milk chocolate and hazelnuts.
